bollywood.title: Bollywood Dreams
bollywood.description: All the romance, drama, and extravagant musical numbers you crave, from Bollywood to your TV

515811.title: Ajab Singh Ki Gajab Kahani
515811.description: The true story of handicapped IRS officer Ajay Kumar Singh, who never let his disabilities define his future, and fought to make India better.

516819.title: Samrat & Company
516819.description: After a local tycoon is murdered, his daughter hires a private investigator to find the killers as his efforts sweep them on a wild ride for justice.

516831.title: Sweety Weds NRI
516831.description: A young Indian woman’s father wants to arrange a marriage between her and an Indian man who isn't a citizen of India and lives in England.

517748.title: Kerry on Kutton
517748.description: The lives of four teenagers on different paths intertwine and spiral into the criminal underworld in the small Indian town of Ballia.

517780.title: Fever
517780.description: Things get tricky for an assassin who wakes from an accident and knows his name but has amnesia in all other areas, including his own fateful crime.

518653.title: Mad About Dance
518653.description: Hopes, dreams, and anxieties about the future are told through stories and dance as a group of Indian students relocate to England for their studies.

518946.title: Jackpot
518946.description: Set entirely in Goa against the backdrop of casino boats, card players involved in a con compete in a high stakes game during one wild monsoon season.

519194.title: Maazii
519194.description: Tarun is a family man these days, but when he inadvertently kills two gangsters, his dark past floods back into the life he worked so hard to build.

525833.title: Yaara Silly Silly
525833.description: A sex worker and her client reunite and discover a relationship that changes their lives forever.

525835.title: 72 Hours
525835.description: Set during the Indo-China war, the real life story of a brave rifleman who fought for 72 hours alone is depicted in this biopic.

528707.title: Hai Apna Dil Toh Awara
528707.description: The lives and power struggles of 3 separate couples in India with their own ideas of life and the way things should be unfold in this romantic comedy.

528709.title: Desi Kattey
528709.description: Explosive action and emotional tension highlight this story of an aspiring competitive shooter and his childhood friend attached to criminal life.

536046.title: Amne Samne
536046.description: Simple-minded Gopi happens to look like popular musician Johnny. After Gopi becomes Johnny’s double, he’s held responsible for the crooner's crimes.

538847.title: Ahankaar
538847.description: After surviving a freak accident which left him mute, a young man struggles to support his family while living a life of self-sacrifice.

539555.title: Mickey Virus
539555.description: A small-time hacker mistakenly commits a robbery when he helps the woman he loves reverse a transaction by hacking her company’s website.

542265.title: Barsaat Ki Ek Raat
542265.description: A married inspector’s joyous life with his pregnant wife is threatened by the lethal intentions of a freed man he had arrested 5 years earlier.

555680.title: Page 16
555680.description: An extramarital affair throws Ajay’s life into chaos when the woman mysteriously dies and he finds a secret about her in a book he buys for his son.

555681.title: Do Aur Do Paanch
555681.description: The kidnapping of a wealthy man’s son for a hefty ransom goes awry when two rival con artists realize they both hatched the same exact plot.

562548.title: Kissebaaz
562548.description: There’s no mercy, no rules, and certainly no trust as a man in the spiritual capital of India becomes the victim of a scheme he never saw coming.

567795.title: Mann
567795.description: Strangers who fall in love on a cruise agree to meet six months after figuring out their careers and romantic bonds at home, but one fails to show up.

567797.title: Dhamaal
567797.description: A dying thief’s last words about a hidden treasure creates a race between four homeless grifters and a greedy police chief to find the loot first.

567799.title: Yeh Lamhe Judaai Ke
567799.description: A man’s dream of being a famed singer comes true after his best friend does her best to help, but his circle of friends tries to make him turn on her.

567801.title: Dil
567801.description: The son of a poor man and the daughter of a proud rich man face the wrath of both sets of parents after they marry in spite of their disapproval.

567803.title: Hadh Kar Di Aapne
567803.description: A comedy of identities and chaos erupts as a detective in Europe on a case falls in love with a woman who is really impersonating her best girlfriend.

567805.title: Jab Pyar Kisi Se Hota Hai
567805.description: A playboy does his best to honor his girlfriend’s request that he stop his reckless antics, but a young boy claiming to be his son changes things.

567809.title: Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage
567809.description: A man ready to marry his girlfriend for love is determined to overcome her fears of loving him back for fear of her conservative family’s backlash.

567810.title: Fight Club: Members Only
567810.description: The law comes down on the heels of four friends implicated in a murder after they start an underground fight club for paid grudge matches.

567812.title: Hello Brother
567812.description: The heart donor who saves a policeman’s life ends up spiritually leading him to try to stop a drug syndicate posing as a local messenger service.

567814.title: Rudraksh
567814.description: A day laborer is possessed by a demon out for world rule after he finds a sacred seed, a goal that a healer, his father and a researcher try to end.

567815.title: Fida
567815.description: When goons threaten a young man’s sweetheart, to extort a huge sum of money, he robs a bank and finds himself entangled in a bigger conspiracy.

567817.title: Maine Pyar Kyun Kiya
567817.description: A surgeon lies about being married to keep women at a distance, so when he finally falls in love, he must conjure up a phony wife and a fake divorce.

568339.title: Hum Kissi Se Kum Nahin
568339.description: A dreaded Mumbai gangster unexpectedly falls in love with a young woman and is forced to consult her elder brother to receive psychiatric help

568341.title: Dil Ka Rishta
568341.description: A man finds his beloved is engaged to another man. When he has a DUI crash that gives her amnesia and kills her fiancé, he isn't sure he can tell her.

568343.title: A Sublime Love Story: Barsaat
568343.description: A car designer on business in the U.S. from India falls for a woman who has no idea he has a wife back home, a revelation that could be devastating.

579594.title: Ek Yodha Shoorveer
579594.description: After his father is murdered by explorer Vasco da Gama, a young man set on vengeance wages a personal war against the Portuguese conquest of India.

595445.title: Chal Mere Bhai
595445.description: A standoffish businessman grieving the death of his girlfriend, falls in love with a vivacious girl working in his office, unaware of the fact that his younger brother is deeply in love with her too.

595447.title: Shool
595447.description: A diligent Police Inspector Samar is transferred to a small town swarming with corruption and moral decay. As he begins to straighten things up, he attracts the unwanted attention of corrupt politician who becomes a threat to Samar and his family.

595449.title: Ek Hi Raasta
595449.description: A terrorist aspiring to rule over India needs vital information about Indian armed forces. He recruits an Indian army officer for this purpose, who goes to great evil lengths to get the treasured information.

595535.title: Prince
595535.description: Prince, a diamond thief, pulls off the robbery of a lifetime. He wakes up one morning and realises that he has lost his memory and his life is at stake.

595734.title: Tango Charlie
595734.description: Tarun, a BSF officer, along with his battalion gets deployed to Kargil when a war between India and Pakistan breaks out. This is where Tarun faces the life-threatening challenge which will decide his fate.

595738.title: Rajaji
595738.description: A gold-digging slacker marries the daughter of a multi-millionaire but abandons her when he realises that she's the daughter of the millionaire's gardener. He, however, tries to woo her again when she wins a life-changing lottery.

595740.title: Mere Do Anmol Ratan
595740.description: Suman happily delivers her baby boy in a hospital. When a fire breaks out in the hospital, she cannot tell her son apart from another infant who has lost his mother. So she decides to take them both home and decide to solve the mystery.

595742.title: Mere Baap Pehle Aap
595742.description: Gaurav takes great care of his widowed father Janardhan who has single-handedly raised him and his brother with love. Soon, when Gaurav falls in love, he finds out about his father's childhood love and insists that Janardhan gets married first.

595743.title: Mera Gaon Mera Desh
595743.description: A petty criminal Ajit redeems himself in a village terrorised by bandits. In the process, he falls in love with a village belle Anju and takes it upon himself to save her and her community, that is being bullied by some dangerous dacoit.

595744.title: Kartoos
595744.description: A cop trains a criminal Raja to end the reign of a deadly underworld don. But the mission falters when Raja falls in love and puts everyone's life and the mission at risk.

595745.title: Kachche Dhaage
595745.description: Aftab and Jai are stepbrothers who loathe each other. They are forced to put their differences aside and work together when they get accused of terrorist activities and government agencies along with mafia get on their tail.

595746.title: Jamai Raja
595746.description: A high-handed millionaire Durgeshwari Devi is disgruntled when her daughter falls in love with a poor man. Hoping to dissuade him from marrying her and taint his reputation, she puts a condition that he'll have to stay with them post marriage.

595748.title: Jaisi Karni Waisi Bharni
595748.description: After swindling his parents of their ancestral home, Vijay sets them astray. Years later, upon learning the truth, his own son plots to teach Vijay and his wife a lesson.

595750.title: Gharana
595750.description: An honest jeweller, Prem Mehra, loses all his wealth and estate when his rival Dharamdas colludes with one his employees and steals his diamonds. It is now left to Prem's sons to get everything back.

595751.title: Champion
595751.description: A burly Inspector is on a quest to wipe off crime. After rigorous police training to eliminate hardened criminals, he is assigned to protect a nine-year-old orphan, who happens to be an heir to millions.

595788.title: Kunwara
595788.description: Raju and Urmila fall for each other in New Zealand and promise to meet in India. On his journey in India, Raju meets pregnant Sharmila. To help her, Raju meets her family as her husband and realises that Sharmila is none other than Urmila's sister.

606405.title: Yoddha
606405.description: A man grows into a warrior as he learns it’s easier to go to war with an enemy across the border than to fight the evil in your own community.

606565.title: 7 Roshan Villa
606565.description: A grieving woman, whose medication makes her hallucinate, goes with her dishonest husband to a remote villa for rest, but murder is on the itinerary.

606641.title: Miranda House
606641.description: When an artist creates a set of five paintings based on the five natural elements, his son tries to stop a nefarious art dealer from obtaining them.

606907.title: Anvatt
606907.description: To honor his late grandfather, a young man and his girlfriend commit to spending a year in a remote village where spooky strange occurrences await.

607050.title: Nilkanth Master
607050.description: The epic story of a young man in India who leaves his home to join a band of revolutionaries to defend their motherland against British rule.

607241.title: Online Binline
607241.description: A charming tale of a man addicted to online apps and the Internet who has to compete with one of his friends for the affections of their mutual crush.

607640.title: Thoda Tuza Thoda Maza
607640.description: The story of a father and son who are trying to come to terms of understanding because of his son’s spoiled and naïve entitlement.

607647.title: Goa 350 KM
607647.description: When their car breaks down en route to their honeymoon, newlyweds are trapped by the ghost of a murdered woman and forced to find her killer, or else!

607853.title: Maat
607853.description: The film adaptation of the Indian novel about the heartfelt bonds between a young and ambitious couple and the upheavals they face with each other.

607986.title: Mukkam Post Dhanori
607986.description: When an archaeology student tries to fulfill her late mother's dream, she and her friends come face-to-face with evil and must unite against a demon.

607987.title: Shortcut
607987.description: A shy, virtuous young tech genius uses algorithms and hacking to impress the girl who stole his heart, but also attracts dangerous criminal attention.

608005.title: Aik
608005.description: A man, who conveniently believes that he loves his unhappy wife and young son more than himself, gets trapped in a haunted creation of his own design.

608213.title: Struggler
608213.description: On the road to Bollywood stardom, an actor from the Marathi theater scene finds cutthroat competition, love, and the ultimate test of his character.

608300.title: Dhurandhar Bhatawdekar
608300.description: Two seniors with polar opposite personalities find themselves locked in a love triangle and duking it out for the affections of a middle-aged woman.

608493.title: Tony: My Mentor the Serial Killer
608493.description: A group of psychology students plant a camera in a church's confession box, but they are unprepared for a killer admitting his crimes.

608540.title: Hirkani
608540.description: Set during the reign of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, the film depicts the story of Hira, a simple village woman. When the gates of Raigad fort shut before she can leave, Hira dares to climb down a cliff in the dead of night to get back to her infant son.

608941.title: Kaashi
608941.description: A murder mystery surrounds two siblings in the cremation ritual city of Benaras, India where they discover that behind every lie is the real truth.

625504.title: Jai Vikraanta
625504.description: In this Hindi revenge film, a noble sugarcane farmer is assassinated when he declines a bribe, causing his son to make sure scores get settled.

625505.title: Inteqam
625505.description: A man seeks revenge on the corrupt lawyer who threw his sister’s rape case by kidnapping the lawyer’s sister and giving her up to a local brothel.

625507.title: Gair Kaanooni
625507.description: A widower whose wife died from the shock of her baby being switched after an abduction uses a convict’s street skills to get justice and answers.

625509.title: Ek Rishtaa: The Bond of Love
625509.description: Bollywood leading men Amitabh Bachchan and Akshay Kumar star in this tale of a father and son whose falling out will require family bonds to prevail.

625511.title: Devar
625511.description: This classic 1966 drama from India takes on the star-crossed and traditional arranged marriage of two people that goes dramatically wrong.

625516.title: Pyaar Diwana Hota Hai
625516.description: This charming Bollywood romantic comedy is about a country boy who moves to the city and pretends to be deaf and mute to win over his big city crush.

625524.title: Love Love Love
625524.description: A passionate and forbidden love story about a taxi driver’s son who falls in love with the daughter of a corrupt man who has other plans for her.

625526.title: Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai
625526.description: A college guy with too much time on his hands falls for his introverted and smart student peer, not knowing she is terrified of her dangerous father.

625599.title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gayaa
625599.description: When an Indian young man goes to rescue his brother, he falls for a Pakistani woman, but their budding romance quickly hits trouble.

625604.title: Phamous
625604.description: When a group of men find themselves caught in the crossfires of a seemingly endless game of revenge, they must decide where their loyalties lie.

626086.title: Rishtey
626086.description: A single father who dotes on his young son is drawn into a devastating child custody battle when the boy’s mother returns years after leaving them.

626604.title: Sharmaji Ki Lag Gayi
626604.description: After an average guy is suddenly given one million rupees, he works with his slacker roommate to track down his mysterious benefactor.

626606.title: Swarag Se Sunder
626606.description: A man and his wife live in peace with his stepbrother and his wife, but when some property issues crop up, the group dynamic shifts.

626611.title: I Proud to Be an Indian
626611.description: When an Indian father and son travel to London for a wedding, they learn that their community is being threatened by white nationalists.

626620.title: Zulmi
626620.description: A man hires a street fighter to look after his daughter, and the two begin a romance. But their relationship is upended by conflicted interests.

626622.title: Zed Plus
626622.description: This hilarious political satire centers on small town bureaucracy, where corruption and mismanagement have destroyed everyday life.

626631.title: Tejaa
626631.description: Three criminals who kill almost an entire family they wrongly believe stole their hidden cash live to regret it when the adult survivor comes to call.

626633.title: Dil Kya Kare
626633.description: Bollywood superstar Ajay Devgn stars as a married adoptive father whose wife doesn’t know that their new nanny is the mother he made the child with.

626637.title: Auzaar
626637.description: Bollywood screen icons Salman Khan, Sanjay Kapoor, Shilpa Shetty star in this drama about best friends with private lives: one legal, one criminal.

626641.title: Charanon Ki Saugandh
626641.description: An indentured servant in 1980s India rebels against his land baron boss in a local election, bringing on the man’s wealth-induced wrath.

626645.title: Majboor
626645.description: When a single lawyer brings home a female ex-convict, his family arranges their marriage until a prisoner interrupts their wedding day with a shock.

626647.title: Jail
626647.description: A corporate worker in India sees his cushy life go up in smoke when he’s falsely accused of selling drugs and sentenced to time in a hardcore prison.

626649.title: Ganga Ki Saugand
626649.description: A brutal man’s atrocities kill a young boy’s mother, and the boy is exiled from his village until he returns as a grown man, ready for revenge.

626690.title: Neel Kamal
626690.description: Classic Bollywood romantic drama about a man who falls for a woman he rescues as she sleepwalks, unaware that she holds dark and unknown past secrets.

627469.title: Kaun Sachha Kaun Jhootha
627469.description: A psychiatrist lands in a professional dilemma when she falls in love with a patient but her secret past keeps her from marrying him once he recovers.

628283.title: Aulad
628283.description: A man who lost his wife in an accident gives their child to a widow who has lost her baby and husband, but he faces a dilemma when his wife returns.

628285.title: Avtaar
628285.description: A selfless, retired car mechanic is forced to start over and succeed at a new business when his cruel sons cheat him and his wife out of their home.

628287.title: Baaz: A Bird in Danger
628287.description: A new white-collar worker in a Northern India town finds himself in the crosshairs of local police hunting for a serial killer targeting young women.

628292.title: Bahurani
628292.description: After a man rejects the plain village girl his parents arranged for him to marry, she revamps herself and comes back into his life as a sophisticate.

628294.title: Banjaran
628294.description: Two star-crossed lovers who have not seen each other since their past lives finally meet and fall in love, but their fathers try to tear them apart.

628295.title: Bemisal
628295.description: Bollywood matinee idol Amitabh Bachchan stars as a humble orphan whose devotion to the foster family that raised him threatens to derail his life.

628297.title: Bhagam Bhag
628297.description: Two immature actors end up involved in a criminal mix-up after their behavior causes their leading lady to quit while they are ordered to replace her.

628301.title: Chhote Sarkar
628301.description: Framed for the murder of his uncle, a respected businessman feigns insanity to buy time while secretly working to find the killer and clear his name.

628303.title: Dil Hai Tumhaara
628303.description: The rivalry between half-sisters Shalu and Nimmi goes next-level when their mother arranges marriage for one with a businessman that the other loves.

628304.title: Ghar Ghar Ki Kahani
628304.description: Suspicions get the worst of Ram as he begins to unravel while quietly observing the relationship between his wife and younger brother grow stronger.

628305.title: Guddu Ki Gun
628305.description: After Guddu cheats on his girlfriend, her grandfather casts a curse on him that can only be broken if he finds true love and manages to stay faithful.

628307.title: Hera Pheri
628307.description: The bond between two best friends and con artists is severed when they uncover secrets from their pasts that unleash a bloody saga of family vengeance.

628310.title: Jaan-E-Mann: Let's Fall in Love… Again
628310.description: To shirk his alimony obligations, Suhaan hatches a scheme to get his ex-wife remarried to an old college friend, which backfires in an unexpected way.

628314.title: Judwaa
628314.description: Years after being separated at birth, a pair of long-lost twins reunite to fight against a common enemy—and one another—for a shared love interest.

628316.title: Kaalia
628316.description: After being framed for murder for refusing to accept a bribe, an honorable man escapes prison to exact revenge on the gangsters who put him there.

628324.title: Mard
628324.description: An Assistant Police Commissioner who gets transferred to a new district for his loyalty to the force comes up against a ruthless local gangster.

628330.title: Bichhoo
628330.description: A soul-haunted hitman takes a young girl in and trains her for revenge when her family is killed by the local mafia, but falls in love with her too.

628372.title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
628372.description: A blind woman regains her sight and lands in a romantic triangle, with the lover who cared for her and an exciting new man, who proposes marriage.

628374.title: Four Two Ka One
628374.description: Jobless friends hope to change their fortunes by stealing a mysterious bag and get entangled in chaos, when others who want its contents give chase.

628694.title: Dharam Veer
628694.description: A man who has heard a prophecy that his oldest nephew will eventually murder him kills one of his sister’s sons and revenge is soon upon him.

629485.title: Pyar Hi Pyar
629485.description: The first investigation for a rookie police constable is finding the missing father of a young woman he winds up falling desperately in love with.

629489.title: Salaakhen
629489.description: When his dad is driven to suicide after testifying in a rape case against a powerful businessman, his son vows revenge against a corrupt justice system.

629490.title: Sangdil Sanam
629490.description: After serving 12 years in prison for a robbery he didn’t commit, a bank manager returns home to learn his own friend was the one who sent him there.

629491.title: Vinashak - Destroyer
629491.description: When police suspect a prison warden is running an illegal arms business and using his convicts as hitmen, an officer goes undercover as a prisoner.

629503.title: Big Brother
629503.description: When his sister is disfigured in an acid attack, a peaceful man is transformed into a vigilante justice warrior for her and other victimized women.

629589.title: Ramji Londonwaley
629589.description: A humble small-town man from India arrives in London for a job and finds that his new boss is dead. He’ll be forced to marry to keep his visa.

629591.title: Raja
629591.description: A young man and woman fall in love, but the woman’s two older brothers resist their love because the man’s family is poor and shares a bitter history.

629593.title: Roti
629593.description: A death row prisoner escapes, passing himself off as a schoolteacher in a small village and soon learns you can never run from your past.

630640.title: Mr Joe B. Carvalho
630640.description: When a clueless detective, hired to bring back the eloped daughter of a businessman, spies on the wrong girl, he is mistaken for a deadly terrorist.

630649.title: Deewane
630649.description: Ajay Devgn and Urmila Matondkar lead a Bollywood romantic drama about a woman whose comatose lover is replaced with a lookalike without her knowledge.

630759.title: Deewane Huye Paagal
630759.description: A murder witness flees India for Dubai, only to have her local crush follow her along with the killer and other men who want her all for themselves.

631430.title: Waqt Hamara Hai
631430.description: Two happy-go-lucky college besties and their girlfriends have to save the fate of the world when they get unknowingly put in a terrorist plot.

631436.title: Sindoor
631436.description: A college professor’s decision to cast his wife out of their house over infidelity concerns comes back to haunt him when they reunite years later.

631438.title: Sau Din Saas Ke
631438.description: A woman tries to make the overbearing rule and control of her cold-hearted mother-in-law things of the past in order to keep the peace and start anew.

631445.title: Naqab
631445.description: A man who sees a mysterious woman singing approaches her and she disappears, only to show up again and again, causing him to doubt his sanity.

631449.title: Masti
631449.description: Three best friends who are over their respective marriages decide it’s time to have affairs, except they end up as framed murder suspects instead.

631453.title: Luck
631453.description: A kingpin develops his own series of life-threatening sports challenges for contestants all over the world – and only one can live to get the prize

631455.title: Lootere
631455.description: A policeman rankles his partner during the investigation of a fellow cop’s murder when he falls in love with the bar dancer who witnessed the crime.

631461.title: Jeet
631461.description: A hitman falls in love with his target’s engaged daughter and turns over a new leaf, but when he backslides—he finds out that her man is his next hit.

631469.title: Amrit
631469.description: Two widowed parents find peace and comfort in each other’s company. Neglected by their selfish children, the two decide to be together on their own.

631471.title: Albela
631471.description: Tourist guide Tony (Govinda) is smitten by a light-eyed beauty Sonia (Aishwarya Rai) who arrives in Goa in search of her mother's grave. Convinced that she's his princess as a soothsayer predicted, Tony tries to woo her.

631473.title: ALAG - He Is Different - He Is Alone
631473.description: An orphan boy, considered strange from his years kept in a basement, is abducted by a rehab scientist for experiments once he displays psychic powers.

631475.title: Aflatoon
631475.description: A grifter with a plan to become an instant millionaire by marrying an heiress gets his plans foiled by a series of crimes committed by his lookalike.

631476.title: Deewangee
631476.description: A criminal lawyer takes the case of an accused murderer as a favor to a beautiful popular singer, but discovers the defendant has a split personality.

631483.title: Chaand Kaa Tukdaa
631483.description: A wealthy man who comes to India to find a soul mate to marry falls in love with a village girl who isn’t as free or safe from danger as he thought.

631485.title: Bumm Bumm Bole
631485.description: A boy who loses his sister’s shoes at the market shares his shoes with her instead of telling their poverty-stricken father and risking his anger.

631489.title: Bewaffa Se Waffa
631489.description: A married woman’s inability to have children leads her to ask her best friend to marry her husband, but her in-laws jump on it and create more chaos.

631491.title: Beta
631491.description: Tensions boil over between the conniving stepmother of a millionaire heir and his new wife who knows that the stepmother is scheming against them.

631496.title: Gundaraj
631496.description: A middle-class man living in the city with his family and lover is framed for the assault of three college girls, leaving his personal life in ruins.

631501.title: Ghar Sansar
631501.description: A man whose father dies is forced to choose between selling off their family estate to pay off his father’s debts or work them off over time.

631502.title: Fun2Shh... Dudes in the 10Th Century
631502.description: A Bollywood comedy about three men, framed for a brazen thief’s royal steal, who time travel between the 10th and 21st century to clear their names.

631504.title: Farishtay
631504.description: The young, grieving widow of a brutally murdered man is sent over the edge when she learns that her brothers work for his killer on the loose.

631506.title: Elaan
631506.description: A police officer whose older son gets killed fails to get justice through proper channels, causing his youngest son to become a vigilante.

631549.title: Andolan
631549.description: A poverty-stricken couple adopt an orphan child to be a brother to their son. As the boys get older, one becomes a scholar and the other a criminal.

631551.title: Dhol
631551.description: Four lazy best friends think they’ll get rich if one of them can get a wealthy young heiress to date them, but instead they land in a murder mystery.

631967.title: Bollywood Beats
631967.description: An aspiring dancer starts a dance class for Indian women that begins to take off just as he’s offered a chance at stardom and must make a big choice.

634532.title: Wife Lover
634532.description: A stormy affair between an ennuied and lonely married woman and the young painter renting her apartment ends in dueling sets of murderous plans.

634554.title: Chameli
634554.description: Over the course of a night in Mumbai’s red light district, an investment banker with car trouble rides out a vicious monsoon with a young sex worker.

634555.title: Bow Barracks Forever
634555.description: Based on the real-life story of a tiny but resolute Anglo-Indian community trying desperately to keep its spirit, identity, and tradition alive.

634557.title: Shabd
634557.description: The line between fiction and reality become dangerously blurred when a novelist looking for inspiration convinces his wife to engage in an affair.

634558.title: Just Married
